<div id="pf4654" class="pf w66 h2f7" data-page-no="4654"><div class="pc pc4654 w66 h2f7"><div class="t md2e x9f h5 y2fd2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 12 September 14-20 </div><div class="t mac1 x1cc h154 y2c70 ff2 fs33 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IE </div><div class="t m5 x27 h154 y2c70 ff2 fs33 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m676 xa h154 y2c76 ff2 fs33 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ig 5cou</div><div class="t m2960 x3c h154 y2c75 ff2 fs33 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m489c x33 h5b y2c66 ff4 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">n2 </div><div class="t m29a xa8 h9e y2c4e ff1 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">AIT2 </div><div class="t m5a3 x1cc h111 y2ab6 ff3 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Urlit </div><div class="t m1045 x5b h9e y2ab6 ff1 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">HEE3002t1 </div><div class="t m2e0 xd0 h5 y2883 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I was given a sharp physical pain </div><div class="t m119 x93 h35 y2091 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rhich </div><div class="t m21d x15 h5 y2380 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">came as Satan&apos;s messenger to </div><div class="t m450 x93 h5 yf11 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ruise me; this was to save me from </div><div class="t m833 x93 h5 yf14 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eing unduly elated. Three times I </div><div class="t m468 x93 h5 y18d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">egged the Lord to rid me of it, but his </div><div class="t m361 x93 h5 y5cc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nswer was: &apos;My grace is all you need; </div><div class="t m92 x93 h5 y1a7e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ower comes to its full strength in </div><div class="t m109 x93 h5 y4be ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;eakness&apos; &quot; (2 Cor. 12:7-9, NEB). </div><div class="t m180 xd0 h35 y557 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;There are cases where God works </div><div class="t m6c9 x93 h35 yd3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ecidedly by His divine power in the </div><div class="t mfab xd0 h35 y5d0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">storation of health. But not all the </div><div class="t m3bc xd6 h35 y25f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ck are healed. Many are laid away to </div><div class="t m19f xd6 h35 y1b5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eep in Jesus. John on the Isle of </div><div class="t m7c2 x93 h35 yfdc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">atmos was bidden to write: &apos;Blessed </div><div class="t m137 x93 h35 y285 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">re the dead which die in the Lord </div><div class="t m1a1 xd6 h35 ye1a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">om henceforth: Yea, saith the Spirit, </div><div class="t m983 x93 h35 y4d4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">iat they may rest from their labors; </div><div class="t m1175 x93 h35 y179 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nd their works do follow them. </div><div class="t m13e x93 h35 ya82 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">evelation 14:13. From this we see that </div><div class="t m5ed xd6 h35 yda6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persons are not raised to health, they </div><div class="t m1c5 x93 h35 y8f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hould not on this account be judged </div><div class="t m14b x93 h35 y5b6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">s wanting in faith.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m69d x40 h35 y5b6 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ministry of </div><div class="t m1ff x1cc h35 y43a ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">!ealing, </div><div class="t m16d x26 h35 y43a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 230. </div><div class="t m6e9 xd0 h35 y87c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job&apos;s experience is an eloquent </div><div class="t ma42 x93 h35 y268 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">xample of unanswered prayer. He </div><div class="t m618 x93 h35 y55d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ried &quot;Why won&apos;t God give me what I  </div><div class="t m1182 x7a h35 y292c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ask? Why won&apos;t he answer my prayer?&quot; </div><div class="t m860 x7a h35 y2090 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 6:8, TEV). And again, &quot;I call to </div><div class="t mb62 x7a h35 y2351 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you, 0 God, but you never answer; </div><div class="t m3d3 x7a h35 y12c1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and when I pray, you pay no attention&quot; </div><div class="t m110a x7a h35 y207 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 30:20, TEV). Job&apos;s problem was </div><div class="t m65d x7a h35 y8ca ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that he didn&apos;t have the information we </div><div class="t m6b4 x7a h35 y945 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have in the first and second chapters </div><div class="t m6b2 x7a h35 y1c6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the book of Job. He was flying blind. </div><div class="t m8fd x7a h35 y374 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He didn&apos;t know that every syllable of </div><div class="t m99 x7a h35 y14b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">his prayers was being heard by a loving </div><div class="t mb47 x52 h35 y7a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God, and would eventually be </div><div class="t m25e x7a h35 y434 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">answered. </div><div class="t m7b5 x90 h35 y2d9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Bible is full of unanswered </div><div class="t m330 x7a h35 yab4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prayers. &quot;Moses prays to enter the </div><div class="t m39a x7a h35 y243 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Promised Land, but dies on Nebo&apos;s </div><div class="t m299 x7a h35 y6ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">top, his request refused. In the midst </div><div class="t mcd1 x7a h35 y1d1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of national calamity the patriot lifts his </div><div class="t m8fb x7a h35 y494 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lamentation, &apos;Thou hast covered </div><div class="t m357 x7a h35 y3bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thyself with a cloud, so that no prayer </div><div class="t ma2 x7a h35 y17a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">can pass through&apos; (Lam. 3:44); and the </div><div class="t me75 x7a h35 y3f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophet Habakkuk in his </div><div class="t m485 x7a h35 ya6f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">despondency exclaims, &apos;0 Jehovah, </div><div class="t m2db x7a h35 y439 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">how long shall I cry, and thou wilt not </div><div class="t m268 x52 h35 y301 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hear?&apos; (Hab. 1:2). Paul prays thrice that </div><div class="t me4 x7a h35 y5d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a vexatious, physical handicap, a </div><div class="t mf58 x7a h35 y1a20 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;thorn in the flesh, which hinders his </div><div class="t m3ed x52 h35 y269 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">missionary labors, may be removed; </div><div class="t mbbe x52 h35 y37c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">but for the rest of his life he is </div><div class="t m16e x52 h35 y2a5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">compelled to make the best of it and </div><div class="t ma82 x52 h35 ye5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">let it make the best of him (II Cor. </div><div class="t m36b x7a h35 y233 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12:9). Even the Master in the Garden </div><div class="t mdfd x52 h35 y6f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prays for release from the appalling </div><div class="t me99 x52 h35 y290 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cup, but goes out to drink it to the </div><div class="t ma75 x52 h35 yc3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dregs.&quot;—Harry Emerson Fosdick, </div><div class="t m7f9 x165 h35 yc3 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The </div><div class="t madf x7a h35 y161 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Meaning of Prayer, </div><div class="t m1b6 x7f h35 y161 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 116, 117. </div><div class="t m14a x52 h5 y1df ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x52 h5 y426 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m411 x58 h5 y426 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Universality of Death </div><div class="t m604 x58 h5 y87f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Heb. 9:27) </div><div class="t m558 x52 h5 y1695 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t mf1 x58 h5 y186 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God Knows Best </div><div class="t m3a2 x58 h5 y380 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 55:8, 9) </div><div class="t mb7 x52 h5 y36f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m22f x58 h5 y36f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Unexpected Ways </div><div class="t m211 x58 h5 y10b1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Phil. 4:19) </div><div class="t m1ce x52 h5 y2ad ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t me3a x58 h5 y2ad ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acting Rationally </div><div class="t m324 x58 h5 y1ae ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(James 1:5) </div><div class="t m8a8 x52 h5 y30c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t mec2 x58 h5 y30c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Learning From Suffering </div><div class="t m434 x58 h5 y445 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(2 Cor. 1:3, 4) </div><div class="t m2ef x52 h5 y395 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t mcdd x58 h5 y395 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Persisting in Prayer </div><div class="t m9b9 x58 h5 yaa6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 12:12) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
